Inequality measures

The cirsis

  • Global financial crisis in 2008.

  • The Greek debt crisis in 2010.

Before that:

  • High level of welfare makes fiscal condition even worse.

  • Fragile economic structure.

  • Severe tax evasion.

  • Mismatch between fiscal and monetary policy.

Fiscal burden

Tax evasion

Economic structure

Rely on agriculture, shipping and tourism sector.

Persisent impact on economics and poverty

  • Major sectors were hit by the global crisis.

  • Government cut the expenditure.

  • Monetary policy was abandoned.
